1711

 

Field identifier (Name):

1711 (REGIONAL ENTITIES)

 

 

Definition:

IDENTIFIES A SPECIFIC POLITICAL OR ADMINISTRATIVE SUB-DIVISION WITHIN A COUNTRY.{THIS FFIRN IS BROKEN AND SHOULD NOT BE USED UNTIL IT HAS BEEN REVISITED BY THE OPERATIONAL SPONSOR}

 

 

Sponsor:

None

 

 

Remarks:

THE AINTP-3 DATA DICTIONARY CONTAINS A LARGE LIST OF DATA ITEMS AND DATA CODES (>3000). WHICH ARE INTENDED TO BE INCORPORATED IN STANAG 1059 NEXT EDITION.

 

 

Related Documents:         

AINTP-3, VOLUME 2 (DATA DICTIONARY)

 

 

Status:  

In Service

 

 

Field Version:

1.0
